<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT18">
<l>māṟāya tāṉavaṉai vaḷḷukirāl mārviraṇṭu</l>
<l>kūṟākak kīṟiya kōḷariyai vēṟāka</l>
<l>vētti yiruppārai vellumē maṟṟavaraic</l>
<l>cārtti yiruppār tavam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The penance of the people who join</l>
<l>those who keep praising in a distinct way</l>
<l>the Lion who sliced the chest of the inimical Rākṣasa into two</l>
<l rend="indent">with [His] sharp claws,</l>
<l>Shall overcome them.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
